    <abstract>
      <t>FMIPv6 extends Mobile IPv6 for reducing handover delays. But it does not deal with the scenario that an MN joins multicast trees using it's CoA in a visited link. The document proposes an extension to FMIPv6 to handle local multicast traffic during handover.</t>
